Dear sir,

   Please find the Re-Answering the below mentioned your query and IST 
response below


    *IST-1 (Credit Limit Override) – Current System*

  * In the *current VB6 ERP*, credit limit handling is controlled by
    *|CRLimitLockFlg|*:
      o *|CRLimitLockFlg = 'Y'|*
        → System *does NOT allow order save* when credit limit is exceeded
        → Order is *blocked and must go through approval process*

------------------------------------------------------------------------


      *User Control / ulevel*

  * ❌ *Override is NOT controlled by |ulevel| in |PP_Passwd|*
  * ❌ *No specific |ulevel| exists for credit limit override*
  * Control is *fully driven by |CRLimitLockFlg|*, not user hierarchy
  * Only Spinning - Bannari Customer used,ERP 7.4 Customer are not used
    as of now

------------------------------------------------------------------------
------------------------------------------------------------------------


    *IST-3 (OfferRateFlg)*

  * Parameter table: *|ig_param|*
  * Field name: *|OfferRateFlg|*


      *Current Usage*

  * ❌ *Not actively used by any customer*
  * Rate and Discount:
      o Available *for all users*
      o ❌ Not restricted by division or product segment

------------------------------------------------------------------------


    *IST-4 (CSM Integration)*

  * ✅ CSM API integration exists in current VB6 system


      *Current Status*

  * Initially used in production by a customer
  * Later *stopped due to system issues (corruption)*
  * Currently:
      o *Not actively used*
      o Customer has *initiated plan to reuse CSM integration*

👉 Conclusion:

  * Exists in system
  * ❌ *Not actively live at any customer site as of now*

------------------------------------------------------------------------


    *IST-5 (TCS Threshold)*

  * Controlled via *|ig_param|*
  * Field: *|tcs_flag| (Y/N)*


      *Current Logic*

  * If |tcs_flag = 'Y'|:
      o System calculates *TCS based on cumulative customer sales value*
      o Logic handled in *stored procedure (KSP_TCSAmountCheckLSales)*


      *Business Rule*

  * As per current implementation:
      o *TCS applied only for Scrap Sales*
  * Threshold is *handled within SP logic (not separately configurable)*

------------------------------------------------------------------------


    *IST-8 (RateDeciPos)*

  * Parameter: *|ig_param.RateDeciPos|*


      *Current Usage*

  * ✅ *Standard value = 2 decimal places*
  * ✔ Same across:
      o All customers
      o All divisions
  * ❌ No division-wise variation

------------------------------------------------------------------------


    *Additional IST Clarifications*


      *IST-7 (Dispatch Instruction Flag)*

  * Table: *|IG_PARAM|*
  * Field: *|Despatch_Instruction|*
  * Controls:
      o Whether system follows:
          + *Despatch Instruction flow (IG_INSBODT)* OR
          + *Direct Despatch flow (IG_BODT)*

------------------------------------------------------------------------


      *IST-10 (Report Footer Configuration)*

  * Used for:
      o DLL-based report printing footer


      *Includes fields like:*

  * Prepared By
  * Checked By
  * Signature section


      *Current Status*

  * ❌ *Not actively required / not in use now*

------------------------------------------------------------------------


      *IST-12 (Auto Mail Function)*

  * Table: *|IG_PARAM|*
  * Field: *|automail| (Y/N)*


      *Logic*

  * If enabled:
      o Fetch email configuration from *|PP_divmas|*
          + SMTP
          + Mail ID
          + Password


      *Current Status*

  * ❌ *Not used by any customer currently*

