            <br>
            <b>2. CustID-based hardcoding — has Stage 0 actually
              resolved this?</b><br>
            Section 11 (Customer Variations) lists 11 customer-specific
            behaviours. Most of these are described against customer
            names rather than ig_param configuration flags. The Summary
            Scorecard in Section 14 itself rates Customer
            Configurability at 3 out of 5 with the note 'mostly
            hard-coded with if-then-else rather than configuration-table
            driven.' This is the same issue that required extensive
            correction in the PO module's PR form, which had 13
