            config name with a recommended default value. The Sales
            Order Section 11 describes what each customer variation does
            but does not say how SPINRISE should handle it. For each of
            the 11 variation rows, please add two columns: the SPINRISE
            config parameter name, and the recommended default for a new
            customer installation.<br>
            <br>
            <b>7. Auto-email flow not sufficiently documented.</b><br>
            Section 1 correctly lists auto-email as a capability.
            Section 12 references it. But the trigger logic
            (CheckAutoMail reads ig_param.AutoMail flag), the export
